snippet.title: Hero Team Playtesting Trailer
snippet.description:
Thanks so much to everyone who tried out the Hero Team demo during Steam Next Fest. This is footage captured during the event livestream. The game is coming out in a few short months so please wishlist it now to be the first to know when it goes live:

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1253410/Hero_Team/
https://twitter.com/HeroTeamGame
https://heroteamgame.com/discord
